            <div class="title">
                His Majesty&#39;s Return From South Africa
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1947-05-12/debates/6c3d0e65-f47c-4332-9295-5428fdedf007/TownAndCountryPlanningBill" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
